name: ⭕️ MLNDR Founders Collection: 004/Katy
description: Meet 9 year old Katy. The family’s treasure ❤️. Just as every other girl, she loves looking cute and still cuddles with mom and dad at nights. She still doesn’t fully understands the world she lives in but she is starting to question many aspects about it. It won’t take long for her to realize that the world isn’t as beautiful as she thinks it is. Set in a dystopian future where natural resources are scarce and pollution is a global problem, the MLNDR Family Series will portray how I see our future as a species if our hunger for non-renewable natural resources continues to grow at the current pace. The Founders collection will be comprised of 6 characters who will play as leading actors in my MLNDR Family series. Holders of this token participate for a chance to win one of 10 NFTs from my props collection.
